WEBVTT

00:01.332 --> 00:03.076
I have something serious to say.

00:04.202 --> 00:06.575
So I'm going to use my serious voice.

00:07.462 --> 00:11.098
At Little Caesars, we've always been serious about quality ingredients.

00:11.545 --> 00:15.253
Making our dough fresh from scratch every day in each store,...

00:16.023 --> 00:18.769
...while some places use factory-made or frozen dough.

00:20.037 --> 00:22.599
You can tell by my serious voice how serious I am.

00:23.553 --> 00:26.072
Seriously, I'm serious.

00:30.025 --> 00:30.728
Pizza, pizza!

